          <m>\ds \iint_\c{R} \cos(x)\sin(2y)\, dA \,  , \qquad \c{R} = \left[0,\frac{\pi}{2}\right] \times \left[0,\frac{\pi}{2}\right]</m>
        </p>
      </exercise>

      <exercise number="15.1.43">
